data.description: ROOM TO EXPAND THIS DIAMOND IN THE ROUGH! FULL LIGHT WALK OUT BASEMENT -FINISHED WOULD DOUBLE THE SF! THIS SWEET WEST ASHEVILLE FIXER ALREADY HAS A NEW ROOF, HICKORY HARD WOOD FLOORS, WOOD BURNING STOVE, COVERED SIDE AND FRONT PORCHES! This vintage cottage is set on a spacious, level lot,  the ample yard is adorned with mature trees, blooming perennials and fertile soil - a gardeners dream!, Bring your dogs, chickens, little ones, friends and family to enjoy this sweet property! NO CITY TAXES, Yet minutes to eclectic shops, eateries, and lively entertainment that West and DT Asheville are famous for!!
